frames.caption: Three adorable raccoons, dressed in sparkling blue and white outfits, huddle together in a snowy setting. They are holding a collection of shiny gold coins and a small device, possibly a camera. The background is adorned with festive decorations, creating a warm and magical atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a group of raccoons in a winter wonderland, surrounded by snow and festive lights. The raccoons are dressed in glittering attire, adding to the enchanting and joyful mood of the setting.

frames.caption: Three adorable raccoons, dressed in sparkling blue attire, gather closely together in a festive setting. They are holding a small device and a handful of golden coins, surrounded by a backdrop of shimmering lights and decorations.
frames.description: The scene depicts a whimsical and festive gathering of raccoons, dressed in glittering outfits, in a winter wonderland setting. The atmosphere is warm and joyful, enhanced by the soft glow of lights and the playful interaction among the raccoons.

summary: Animals: raccoons. Nature: snow. Objects: coins, device, decorations. Actions: holding, huddling, gathering. Emotions: joyful, enchanted, playful. Scenes: winter wonderland, festive. Concepts: togetherness, celebration
